{"tid":2452963,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"14歲女童前年荃灣非法集結罪成 羅德泉判處2年感化令","createTime":"2021-03-19T07:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T08:27:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4dc85f3430db18534750497f9c9698147f4dea81","tid":2452963,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:04:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14518&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=95545f75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14518</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第八庭 #少年法庭 #庭外消息<br />\n#羅德泉主任裁判官<br />\n#1013荃灣 #判刑<br />\n#非法集結<br />\n<br />\nD2: 14歲手足<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) 參與非法集結<br />\n被控於2019年10月13日，在荃灣南豐中心外參與非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n📌 重溫裁判官上次尖銳質疑 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13993\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13993&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=3bc82c60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13993</a>)<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n速報：判24個月感化令🛑<br />\n（詳情後補）"},{"pid":"6db808c5e6e01fff99fdaddff140579424824271","tid":2452963,"uid":184261,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:04:56.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢，大波驊最憎感化<br />\n希望佢冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f6df53d87d98750d2a6f16dedb50dbef6ebc53","tid":2452963,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:05:47.000Z","msg":"一早判咁重 一單咁輕<br />\n<br />\n真係唔識捉摸"},{"pid":"bd0c15a74de5b489d591e9f0408189ffc27a7f4b","tid":2452963,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:07:02.000Z","msg":"14歲真係唔適合出黎<img src=\"